<!-- wp:paragraph {"align":"center"} -->
<p class="has-text-align-center">The IOU mission is to improve lives through learning. Our global marketplace features extensive, multi-language courses taught by expert instructors. You can take courses across a wide range of categories, some of which include: business &amp; entrepreneurship, programming, academics, the arts, health &amp; fitness, language, music, and much more!</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->


<div class="wp-block-qubely-text aligncenter qubely-block-3ec728">
    <div class="qubely-block-text  ">
