            <div class="wp-block-qubely-accordion-item qubely-block-b5f951"><div class="qubely-accordion-item qubely-type-fill false"><div class="qubely-accordion-panel qubely-icon-position-right"><span class="qubely-accordion-panel-handler" role="button"><span class="qubely-accordion-panel-handler-label">Can I choose any topic to develop a course?</span><span class="qubely-accordion-icon fa fa-plus"></span></span></div><div class="qubely-accordion-body"><div itemprop="text"><!-- wp:paragraph -->
                            <p>You are free to choose the topic you wish to teach on IOU, but before that, you are kindly requested to analyze the market demand and choose a skill-based topic to work on.</p>
                            <!-- /wp:paragraph --></div></div></div></div>
            <!-- /wp:qubely/accordion-item -->

